# ── Dropped-in compiled harnesses ────────────────────────────────────────────
# Each shape's harness/ folder is where a user drops their compiled bundle.
# Those artifacts are per-user and must not be committed — keep only the
# placeholder that explains what goes there.
*/harness/*
!*/harness/DROP_COMPILED_FILES_HERE.md

# ── Dependencies & lockfiles (generated when a harness is run) ────────────────
node_modules/
.bun/
bun.lock
bun.lockb
package-lock.json
yarn.lock
pnpm-lock.yaml

# ── Secrets ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# cf-worker shapes read ANTHROPIC_API_KEY (and friends) from harness/.dev.vars.
# Never commit credentials.
.dev.vars
*.env
.env
.env.*

# ── OS / editor cruft ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*~
.idea/
.vscode/
*.log
